Gentlemen, and Ladies, a simple proposal (perhaps?)<br><br>
We, and I definately include me in this, seem to have evolved into a seperate &quot;chat&quot; or discussion item.  It is not my desire to be a group leader, rather a participant, but should we not be out from under the label of Viet Nam Protest on our host's site?  I can appreciate that the site loves this interaction, and I am thankful for their hosting, but perhaps a new catagory is in order, if not a new location, if not a new title?  How about under &quot;dialogue&quot; as we are now, we become the &quot;Ongoing Issues Group&quot;??  A leaderless and unhosted place where all are welcomed and all thoughts considered.  I think we are way beyond the simplistic title of &quot;protests&quot;.  Any thoughts out there?  You know, us shrinks like to file our folders correctly, right?<br><br>
